author: cms-l1t-offline
body:
Brings L1T up-to-date with l1t-tsg-v7-cand.

Most notably, updates to Muon TF emulations that improve agreement with hardware, plus updates to BMTF and EMTF unpackers.  Minor updates to improve agreement in other modules.

This version has new large files removed (even from history).  It will not pass tests until external request 
https://github.com/cms-data/L1Trigger-L1TMuon/pull/5 is in the IB.  For testing, a PR with these data files added locally is here:  #14565.
title: Update L1T to l1t-tsg-v7-cand performance (81x)
